channel.title: More human remains found at the 9/11 site.
channel.description:
So more human remains have been found in and around Ground Zero, some 9 years after the original attacks.
it seems that in this case, some of the body parts are large and can be identified to specific victims of the attack. Medical examiners are taking a look at some of them.
[url]https://www.metro.co.uk/news/832499-remains-of-72-found-at-9-11-site[/url]

item.dc:creator: mattemuse
item.description:
And I’m just saying that’s an incredibly stupid analogy, because making an effort to clean up 4 city blocks worth of collapsed is not equivalent to removing all evidence of history’s largest war from an entire country. Didn’t we already have a talk about your analogies in another thread?

In case i’m not making myself sufficiently clear THE TOWERS SHOULD HAVE BEEN REBUILT BY NOW, OR TURNED INTO A MEMORIAL PARK, OR SOMETHING. It’s unbelievable to me that they are still clearing rubble away a decade later, for fucks sake. Apparently nobody else thinks that’s significant. Maybe they are waiting until the economic and geopolitical fallout fixes itself, and then they can finish cleaning up the actual site?
